      <main class="site-main">
        <div id="intro" class="section block-default align-c-xs-max">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row row-table">
              <div class="col-sm-12">
                <div class="col-inner">
                  <div class="section-heading">
                    <h2>Hour of Code!</h2>
                    <p>
                      Today you'll learn about <b>Hour of Code</b> and how to implement it in your classroom. This website will live here forever, so you can some back and use
                      these resources whenever you want :)
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      If there's some typos, I apologize, but you can correct
                      them <a target='_blank' href='https://github.com/jeffthemaximum/Teachers-Dont-Pay-Jeff'>here</a> if you want.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                      You can learn more about me <a target='_blank' href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/jeffmaxim/'>here!</a>
                    </p>
                    <h4>
                      tl;dr
                    </h4>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        What is Hour of Code?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        What can I do for Hour of Code?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        What are the associated standards?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Why teach coding?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        How does coding progress from K-5 and beyond?
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        You don't have to know how to code to teach how to code!
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        No connection to math skills. Many kids will surprise you. No "special" intellectual ability needed.
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Coding vs. Computer Science
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        Doing and Discovery works best
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        How to keep momentum after Hour of Code?
                      </li>

                    </ul>
                  </div> <!-- .section-heading -->
                </div>
              </div>
